props.totalVisible: Specify the total visible pagination numbers
props.firstIcon: The icon to use for the first button
props.prevIcon: The icon to use for the prev button
props.nextIcon: The icon to use for the next button
props.lastIcon: The icon to use for the last button
props.currentPageAriaLabel: Label for the currently selected page
props.firstAriaLabel: Label for the go to first button
props.lastAriaLabel: Label for the go to last button
props.color: Applies specified color to the selected page button - supports utility colors (for example `success` or `purple`) or css color (for example `success` or `purple`) or css color (`#033` or `rgba(255, 0, 0, 0.5)`). Find a list of built-in classes on the [colors page](/styles/colors#material-colors)
props.ellipsis: Text to show between page buttons when truncating the list
props.showFirstLastPage: Show buttons for going to first and last page

events.first: Emitted when clicking on go to first button
events.previous: Emitted when clicking on go to previous button
events.next: Emitted when clicking on go to next button
events.last: Emitted when clicking on go to last button
